      "body" : "You will need to identify what exception is being thrown from the <code>static</code> block. To debug it put a <code>try&#47;catch(Exception e)</code> around the entire block and log the exception. You&#39;ll have to fix that exception. Typically the exception will be logged but may be hard to find since it&#39;s being logged during classloading which may happen very early"
