      "body" : "Failed to initialize ClassA is a side effect from something else. You will want to look at the <code>cause</code> if available. A <code>NoClassDefFoundError</code> is always associated to another error, you will need to look for it in the logs or try to log it more appropriately (like force the logging into a new file on the file system)"
