      "creation_date" : 1446004511,
      "post_id" : 33382605,
      "comment_id" : 54558702,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "What&#39;s more, when the code runs on the linux machine, follow the error above, there is another problem : <code>java.lang.ExceptionInInitializerError: null</code>, it means that can not find the class in the classloader, or don&#39;t know to load which one(I guess). Did you meet that?"
